<br>
<br>
<br>
Father Johnson wiped the sweat off his wrinkled, weather-worn brow. His belly was round, and his arms were as weak as a girl's, but that was okay for a man of faith;<br>
<br>
He could find pleasure other ways.<br>
<br>
