<br>
&quot;Yes yes, I understand. What was your sin, young one?&quot;<br>
<br>
She tilted her head to the side, &quot;Heehee. Oh yea. Well, um... we were all kind of... umm...&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;Horny? It's okay, I've heard the word before.&quot;<br>
<br>
